  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <p><img src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=4d99b1b2&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2FcAd6ObKOzECscRhoNoINWslUiaF8lWmj9YxtFbL9KQPvqpr7Fzyicf1ibFebWfbfGjcaTg5ojhFgr1uTjBusyaZNQ%2F0%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg\"></p>\n  <h2 data-style=\"outline: 0px; text-wrap: wrap; font-family: -apple-system-font, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, sans-serif; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; text-align: center; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); visibility: visible;\" class=\"js_darkmode__4\" style=\"outline:0px;text-wrap:wrap;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:normal;font-family:-apple-system-font, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, sans-serif;line-height:25.6px;text-align:center;\"><span data-style=\"outline: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-weight: bold; font-size: 18px; visibility: visible;\" class=\"js_darkmode__5\" style=\"outline:0px;visibility:visible;font-weight:bold;font-size:18px;\"><span leaf=\"\">奇舞推荐</span></span></h2>\n  <h2 data-style=\"outline: 0px; text-wrap: wrap; font-family: -apple-system-font, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, sans-serif; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; text-align: center; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); visibility: visible;\" class=\"js_darkmode__6\" style=\"outline:0px;text-wrap:wrap;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:normal;font-family:-apple-system-font, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, sans-serif;line-height:25.6px;text-align:center;\"><span data-style=\"outline: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-size: 18px; visibility: visible;\" class=\"js_darkmode__7\" style=\"outline:0px;visibility:visible;font-size:18px;\"><span data-style=\"outline: 0px; color: rgb(255, 218, 81); font-size: 12px; font-family: 微软雅黑; line-height: 28.4444px; white-space-collapse: preserve; visibility: visible;\" class=\"js_darkmode__8\" style=\"outline:0px;visibility:visible;font-size:12px;font-family:微软雅黑;line-height:28.4444px;\"><span leaf=\"\">■</span></span><span data-style=\"outline: 0px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-size: 12px; font-family: 微软雅黑; line-height: 28.4444px; white-space-collapse: preserve; visibility: visible;\" class=\"js_darkmode__9\" style=\"outline:0px;visibility:visible;font-size:12px;font-family:微软雅黑;line-height:28.4444px;\"><span style=\"outline: 0px;color: rgb(217, 33, 66);visibility: visible;\"><span leaf=\"\">■</span></span></span><span style=\"outline: 0px;color: rgb(61, 167, 66);font-size: 12px;font-family: 微软雅黑;line-height: 28.4444px;visibility: visible;\"><span leaf=\"\">■</span></span></span></h2>\n  <div data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" data-website=\"https://www.mdnice.com\" style=\"background-size:auto;background-attachment:scroll;padding-left:10px;letter-spacing:0em;font-size:16px;line-height:1.5em;background-position:0% 0%;background-repeat:no-repeat;word-spacing:0em;background-clip:border-box;word-break:break-word;width:auto;font-family:Optima, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, PingFangSC-regular, serif;background-image:none;background-origin:padding-box;margin-bottom:0px;padding-right:10px;text-align:left;\">\n   <div style=\"padding:0px 8px;letter-spacing:0.03em;font-size:15px;font-family:-apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75;text-align:left;\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\">\n    <p style=\"margin: 1em 0px;line-height: 1.75;font-size: 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><a class=\"normal_text_link\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(145, 109, 213);text-decoration: none;border-bottom: 1px dotted rgb(200, 182, 226);\" href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzU1ODEzNjI2NA==&amp;mid=2247574876&amp;idx=1&amp;sn=4b0bf1c1da0a1c3cd626ec6c308cb579&amp;scene=21#wechat_redirect\" textvalue=\"\" linktype=\"text\" data-linktype=\"2\">AI在泛前端领域的思考和实践-上篇</a></span></p>\n    <p style=\"margin: 1em 0px;line-height: 1.75;font-size: 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\">深度剖析AI对前端开发的影响：界面从GUI向LUI（自然语言界面）迁移、企业服务从网页向API（MCP Server）迁移、程序员能力从\"复制应用\"向\"突破创新\"迁移。文章通过实际案例展示AI Agent如何自主操作网页完成复杂任务，强调未来前端开发者需掌握大模型基础知识、提升思维能力并主动适应技术架构升级。</span></p>\n    <p style=\"margin: 1em 0px;line-height: 1.75;font-size: 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><a class=\"normal_text_link\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(145, 109, 213);text-decoration: none;border-bottom: 1px dotted rgb(200, 182, 226);\" href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=Mzg2OTYyODU0NQ==&amp;mid=2247521105&amp;idx=1&amp;sn=a9441400967442122bdf422aa2ba6521&amp;scene=21#wechat_redirect\" textvalue=\"\" linktype=\"text\" data-linktype=\"2\">Ant Design 发布 Markdown 渲染器 X-Markdown</a></span></p>\n    <p style=\"margin: 1em 0px;line-height: 1.75;font-size: 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\">Ant Design推出专为AI流式对话优化的Markdown渲染器，通过缓存与智能补全机制实现零闪烁增量渲染。基于marked构建，支持LaTeX公式、Mermaid图表等插件生态，采用DOMPurify过滤保障XSS安全。性能测试显示在长文本场景下内存占用较竞品降低50%，帧率稳定性更优，适合高负载AI应用场景。</span></p>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n  <h2 data-style=\"outline: 0px; text-wrap: wrap; font-family: -apple-system-font, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, sans-serif; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; text-align: center; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); visibility: visible;\" class=\"js_darkmode__4\" style=\"outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:normal;font-family:-apple-system-font, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, sans-serif;line-height:25.6px;text-align:center;\"><span data-style=\"outline: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-weight: bold; font-size: 18px; visibility: visible;\" class=\"js_darkmode__5\" style=\"outline:0px;visibility:visible;font-weight:bold;font-size:18px;\"><span leaf=\"\">技术实践</span></span></h2>\n  <h2 data-style=\"outline: 0px; text-wrap: wrap; font-family: -apple-system-font, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, sans-serif; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; text-align: center; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); visibility: visible;\" class=\"js_darkmode__6\" style=\"outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:normal;font-family:-apple-system-font, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, sans-serif;line-height:25.6px;text-align:center;\"><span data-style=\"outline: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-size: 18px; visibility: visible;\" class=\"js_darkmode__7\" style=\"outline:0px;visibility:visible;font-size:18px;\"><span data-style=\"outline: 0px; color: rgb(255, 218, 81); font-size: 12px; font-family: 微软雅黑; line-height: 28.4444px; white-space-collapse: preserve; visibility: visible;\" class=\"js_darkmode__8\" style=\"outline:0px;visibility:visible;font-size:12px;font-family:微软雅黑;line-height:28.4444px;\"><span leaf=\"\">■</span></span><span data-style=\"outline: 0px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-size: 12px; font-family: 微软雅黑; line-height: 28.4444px; white-space-collapse: preserve; visibility: visible;\" class=\"js_darkmode__9\" style=\"outline:0px;visibility:visible;font-size:12px;font-family:微软雅黑;line-height:28.4444px;\"><span style=\"outline: 0px;color: rgb(217, 33, 66);visibility: visible;\"><span leaf=\"\">■</span></span></span><span style=\"outline: 0px;color: rgb(61, 167, 66);font-size: 12px;font-family: 微软雅黑;line-height: 28.4444px;visibility: visible;\"><span leaf=\"\">■</span></span></span></h2>\n  <div data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" data-website=\"https://www.mdnice.com\" style=\"background-size:auto;background-attachment:scroll;padding-left:10px;letter-spacing:0em;font-size:16px;line-height:1.5em;background-position:0% 0%;background-repeat:no-repeat;word-spacing:0em;background-clip:border-box;word-break:break-word;width:auto;font-family:Optima, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, PingFangSC-regular, serif;background-image:none;background-origin:padding-box;margin-bottom:0px;padding-right:10px;text-align:left;\">\n   <div style=\"padding:0px 8px;letter-spacing:0.03em;font-size:15px;font-family:-apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75;text-align:left;\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\">\n    <p style=\"margin: 1em 0px;line-height: 1.75;font-size: 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><a class=\"normal_text_link\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(145, 109, 213);text-decoration: none;border-bottom: 1px dotted rgb(200, 182, 226);\" href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=Mzg3Njc0NTgwMg==&amp;mid=2247503836&amp;idx=1&amp;sn=d84b2e1c6ce9330751cd4d58b3ec32ef&amp;scene=21#wechat_redirect\" textvalue=\"\" linktype=\"text\" data-linktype=\"2\">从JS云函数到MCP：打造跨平台AI Agent工具的工程实践</a></span></p>\n    <p style=\"margin: 1em 0px;line-height: 1.75;font-size: 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\">构建AI工具能力层的完整演进路径：从Flowise的StructuredTool到在线JS云函数平台，最终接入MCP协议实现跨平台调用。核心创新在于通过NodeVM沙箱执行用户代码，自动注入内网能力，将\"写一个JS函数\"转化为\"给AI加新能力\"。方案解决了AI工具复用难、接口参数映射复杂等痛点，实现工具资产化。</span></p>\n    <p style=\"margin: 1em 0px;line-height: 1.75;font-size: 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><a class=\"normal_text_link\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(145, 109, 213);text-decoration: none;border-bottom: 1px dotted rgb(200, 182, 226);\" href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzU2NjU3Nzg2Mg==&amp;mid=2247547486&amp;idx=1&amp;sn=d9c0f1200b8c5616e7dcd98ff372b2b4&amp;scene=21#wechat_redirect\" textvalue=\"\" linktype=\"text\" data-linktype=\"2\">【错误监控】别只做工具人了！手把手带你写一个前端错误监控 SDK</a></span></p>\n    <p style=\"margin: 1em 0px;line-height: 1.75;font-size: 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\">前端错误监控SDK实战教程，完整覆盖\"监听-收集-上报\"核心链路。通过Hook原生方法实现无侵入监控，采用sendBeacon保障页面卸载时数据可靠上报，提供Vue/React框架集成方案。从架构设计到NPM发布的完整工程化实践，是理解监控底层原理的优质入门材料。</span></p>\n    <p style=\"margin: 1em 0px;line-height: 1.75;font-size: 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><a class=\"normal_text_link\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(145, 109, 213);text-decoration: none;border-bottom: 1px dotted rgb(200, 182, 226);\" href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MjM5ODYwMjI2MA==&amp;mid=2649797479&amp;idx=1&amp;sn=66c3c13d139005fbef8a6245d2bb0a44&amp;scene=21#wechat_redirect\" textvalue=\"\" linktype=\"text\" data-linktype=\"2\">AI研发新范式：基于技术方案全链路生成代码</a></span></p>\n    <p style=\"margin: 1em 0px;line-height: 1.75;font-size: 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\">标准化AI编程范式：技术方案模板化→Prompt模板化→代码生成→AI自我总结。通过制定三层技术规范（安全/工程/代码）、四层架构模板（结构/控制器/业务/持久层），将70%+需求转为AI实现，代码采纳率超50%。核心创新是把面向人的技术方案转为AI可执行的指令体系。</span></p>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n  <h2 data-style=\"outline: 0px; text-wrap: wrap; font-family: -apple-system-font, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, sans-serif; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; text-align: center; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); visibility: visible;\" class=\"js_darkmode__4\" style=\"outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:normal;font-family:-apple-system-font, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, sans-serif;line-height:25.6px;text-align:center;\"><span style=\"font-weight:bold;font-size:18px;\"><span leaf=\"\">拓展边界</span></span></h2>\n  <h2 data-style=\"outline: 0px; text-wrap: wrap; font-family: -apple-system-font, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, sans-serif; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; text-align: center; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); visibility: visible;\" class=\"js_darkmode__6\" style=\"outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:normal;font-family:-apple-system-font, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, sans-serif;line-height:25.6px;text-align:center;\"><span data-style=\"outline: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-size: 18px; visibility: visible;\" class=\"js_darkmode__7\" style=\"outline:0px;visibility:visible;font-size:18px;\"><span data-style=\"outline: 0px; color: rgb(255, 218, 81); font-size: 12px; font-family: 微软雅黑; line-height: 28.4444px; white-space-collapse: preserve; visibility: visible;\" class=\"js_darkmode__8\" style=\"outline:0px;visibility:visible;font-size:12px;font-family:微软雅黑;line-height:28.4444px;\"><span leaf=\"\">■</span></span><span data-style=\"outline: 0px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-size: 12px; font-family: 微软雅黑; line-height: 28.4444px; white-space-collapse: preserve; visibility: visible;\" class=\"js_darkmode__9\" style=\"outline:0px;visibility:visible;font-size:12px;font-family:微软雅黑;line-height:28.4444px;\"><span style=\"outline: 0px;color: rgb(217, 33, 66);visibility: visible;\"><span leaf=\"\">■</span></span></span><span style=\"outline: 0px;color: rgb(61, 167, 66);font-size: 12px;font-family: 微软雅黑;line-height: 28.4444px;visibility: visible;\"><span leaf=\"\">■</span></span></span></h2>\n  <div style=\"padding:0px 8px;letter-spacing:0.03em;font-size:15px;font-family:-apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75;text-align:left;\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\">\n   <p style=\"margin: 1em 0px;line-height: 1.75;font-size: 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><a class=\"normal_text_link\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(145, 109, 213);text-decoration: none;border-bottom: 1px dotted rgb(200, 182, 226);\" href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzAxNDEwNjk5OQ==&amp;mid=2650542043&amp;idx=1&amp;sn=2da4173e8fc94e55f31ffd01f4f8f67a&amp;scene=21#wechat_redirect\" textvalue=\"\" linktype=\"text\" data-linktype=\"2\">AI编码实践：从Vibe Coding到SDD</a></span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 1em 0px;line-height: 1.75;font-size: 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\">AI编程演进：从代码补全到Agent Coding，再到基于Rules的约束编程，最终探索SDD（规格驱动开发）。实践发现SDD虽理念先进但落地门槛高，当前最佳实践是\"轻量技术方案+Rules约束+Agent实现+AI文档汇总\"的融合策略，兼顾规范性与开发效率。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 1em 0px;line-height: 1.75;font-size: 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><a class=\"normal_text_link\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(145, 109, 213);text-decoration: none;border-bottom: 1px dotted rgb(200, 182, 226);\" href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzIzOTU0NTQ0MA==&amp;mid=2247556406&amp;idx=1&amp;sn=efcb4798ae9d3d9ddde058d4f0e6945e&amp;scene=21#wechat_redirect\" textvalue=\"\" linktype=\"text\" data-linktype=\"2\">Claude Skills｜将 Agent 变为领域专家</a></span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 1em 0px;line-height: 1.75;font-size: 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\">深度解析Anthropic的Claude Skills机制：通过文件系统实现可复用的知识包，采用渐进式披露原则分三层加载（元数据/指令/资源）。Skills与MCP协议协同工作，为Agent注入领域知识的同时提供标准化工具调用能力，预示工业级Agent将标配可插拔的专家知识模块。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 1em 0px;line-height: 1.75;font-size: 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><a class=\"normal_text_link\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(145, 109, 213);text-decoration: none;border-bottom: 1px dotted rgb(200, 182, 226);\" href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzI2NDU4OTExOQ==&amp;mid=2247693555&amp;idx=1&amp;sn=90cff83d243dd89735aea8afad5d2c07&amp;scene=21#wechat_redirect\" textvalue=\"\" linktype=\"text\" data-linktype=\"2\">Multi-Agent全面爆发！一文详解多智能体核心架构及LangGraph框架</a></span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 1em 0px;line-height: 1.75;font-size: 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\">LangGraph框架核心能力：通过有向图模型重构Agent工作流，支持状态持久化、时间旅行、人机协作等高级功能。重点对比Supervisor（中心化）与Swarm（去中心化）两种多智能体架构，提供Java版本LangGraph4j的完整实践，为构建企业级多智能体系统提供技术选型指南。</span></p>\n  </div>\n  <p data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" data-style=\"padding-top: 8px; padding-bottom: 8px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 0.544px; white-space: normal; text-size-adjust: auto; font-size: 14px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; caret-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); line-height: 26px; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\" mp-original-font-size=\"14\" mp-original-line-height=\"26\" style=\"caret-color:rgb(0, 0, 0);padding-top:8px;text-size-adjust:inherit;letter-spacing:0.544px;padding-bottom:8px;font-size:14px;line-height:26px;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin-bottom:0px;text-align:center;\"><span data-raw-text=\" \" data-textnode-index=\"447\" data-index=\"8540\" mp-original-font-size=\"15\" mp-original-line-height=\"26\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;color: rgb(153, 153, 153);font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0px;line-height: 26px;\"><span data-raw-text=\"-\" mp-original-font-size=\"15\" mp-original-line-height=\"26\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;line-height: 26px;\"><span leaf=\"\">-</span></span><span data-raw-text=\"&nbsp;\" mp-original-font-size=\"15\" mp-original-line-height=\"26\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;line-height: 26px;\"><span data-raw-text=\"E\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\">E</span></span><span data-raw-text=\"N\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\">N</span></span></span><span leaf=\"\">D -</span></span></p>\n </body>\n</html>",
  "aiSummary": "本期奇舞周刊精选了 AI 在前端领域和 Agent 开发方面的多篇技术文章，旨在为技术从业者提供全面的理论洞察和实践指导，涵盖 AI 对前端模式的影响、AI 工具构建、前端错误监控、AI 编程范式、Agent 领域专家化以及多智能体架构等前沿话题。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "本期奇舞周刊精选了 AI 在前端领域和 Agent 开发方面的多篇技术文章，旨在为技术从业者提供全面的理论洞察和实践指导，涵盖 AI 对前端模式的影响、AI 工具构建、前端错误监控、AI 编程范式、Agent 领域专家化以及多智能体架构等前沿话题。",
